00:20:40,673 --> 00:20:42,108
with a product he believes

00:20:42,108 --> 00:20:45,678
is like a vacation
for your feet.

00:20:45,678 --> 00:20:46,445
[ chuckles ]

00:20:46,445 --> 00:20:47,079
[ chuckles ]

00:20:51,217 --> 00:20:53,185
Hi. My name is Pat Yates.

00:20:53,185 --> 00:20:55,121
